We haven't implemented this in an android application yet, so for now the only things that are needed to is a python environment. 
You need to have the kivy library installed.

kivy
kivymd
kivy-deps.angle
kivy-deps.glew
kivy-deps.gstreamer
kivy-deps.sdl2

